            </div>
            <div class="sdg-card">
                <div class="sdg-badge sdg-9">SDG 9</div>
                <h3>Industry, Innovation &amp; Infrastructure</h3>
                <p>Lightweight model deployment on the web brings cutting-edge deep-learning infrastructure outside the hospital, supporting digital health innovation in both developed and developing regions.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="sdg-card">
                <div class="sdg-badge sdg-10">SDG 10</div>
                <h3>Reduced Inequalities</h3>
                <p>By offering a free, web-based screening tool, Skinalyze bridges the healthcare gap between urban specialists and rural populations who lack access to specialist dermatology care.</p>
            </div>
